com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.output.kafka

Class KafkaWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.output.BaseOutputWriter
      • com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.output.kafka.KafkaWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OutputWriter, OutputWriterFactory, AutoCloseable

    @NotThreadSafe
public class KafkaWriter
extends BaseOutputWriter
    This low latency and thread safe output writer sends data to a kafka topics in JSON format. Kafka Topics can be passed as separated by commas such as kafka01,kafka02.
    Author:
    : utkarsh bhatnagar
